	CALL CENTER REPRESENTATIVE<br />
	Part of our mission is to hire the best talent in support of being the employer of choice. Our goal is to be the best at providing a world class customer experience so we are looking for the best employees and talent to join our team and enjoy the ride to the top.</p>
<p>
	<br />
	SUMMARY POSITION<br />
	Spark Networks (www.spark.net) is seeking an educated and experienced customer support/ sales agent for our call center in Provo, Utah. This position requires someone who is highly organized, has excellent communication and follow-through, and can use good-judgment. Highly motivated individuals who are passionate about quality, world-class service, and have superior interpersonal skills are encouraged to apply.<br />
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
