	<li>
		Option of working from home</li>
	<li>
		PT and FT opportunities with potential for growth</li>
	<li>
		Flexible and fun working environment</li>
	<li>
		Casual dress</li>
</ul>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	RESPONSIBILITIES</p>
<ul>
	<li>
